id=one35-no-system-buttons
name=One35 No System Buttons
version=v1
versionCode=1
author=theycallmeboxy via Claude
description=Disables Android system button injection on the MagicX One35. Sets keycodetype=2 on boot so face buttons are pure gamepad inputs with no DPAD_CENTER or Back key injection. Fixes double-input in apps like Cannoli.
updateJson=